{"tid":2317130,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"市民對聖誕未必能外出無奈　飲食業料本月失六成半生意","createTime":"2020-12-08T10:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T11:56:40.000Z","uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"361f82b0e3735bcbf0b6c850d6146a1b6b30aa43","tid":2317130,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"市民對聖誕未必能外出無奈 飲食業料本月失六成半生意<br />\n<br />\n政府公布收緊社交距離措施，包括晚市禁堂食，有市民對聖誕節未必能外出慶祝感到無奈和不開心；餐飲業界預計12月份生意會有6成半跌幅，涉及75億至80億元的生意損失。<br />\n<br />\n有美容業界說，擔心一直停業會令2至3成美容業處所結業；健身業界說新措施是最不理想的「聖誕禮物」，連同這次措施，今年已有近4個月停業。"},{"pid":"7a4bc2c6af79e6c963e27097d89e31d02a726b88","tid":2317130,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564242-20201208.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564242-20201208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=33c94fd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564242-20201208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8d5197d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564242-20201208.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"983659f5731d1613b4f83ada013f106a9c4b12fd","tid":2317130,"uid":45788,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:41:58.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6c4b16d3ab4b76b570c6a1618a3a5ec23130f6","tid":2317130,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:42:37.000Z","msg":"她：企硬，唔封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2bd69f1135c7